ilter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Bayern Munich, Karl-Heinz Rummenigge th\u00ec HLV Thomas Tuchel \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>Bayern nh\u1eafm Thomas Tuchel thay Jupp Heynckes</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/bayern-munich-1567.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Bayern Munich</strong></span> \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Jupp Heynckes. Kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n v\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Ancelotti c\u00f2n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, l\u00fac n\u00e0y &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo; \u0111ang ch\u01a1i th\u0103ng hoa v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u. H\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bundesliga m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, c\u00f2n \u1edf Champions League \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cuc nong HLV Thomas Tuchel da tim duoc ben do moi hinh anh\" title=\"C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng HLV Thomas Tuchel \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/4/13/Cuc-nong-HLV-Thomas-Tuchel-da-tim-duoc-ben-do-moi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Thomas Tuchel l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Jupp Heynckes s\u1ebd chia tay Bayern Munich v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. \u00d4ng n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo; g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, khi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng s\u1ebd chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c. Heynckes n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 72 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Bayern trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t HLV m\u1edbi. C\u1ef1u HLV c\u1ee7a Dortmund, Thomas Tuchel \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 thay th\u1ebf cho Jupp Heynckes. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Bundesliga, \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Bayern t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Thomas Tuchel \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Bayern Munich, Karl-Heinz Rummenigge th\u00ec HLV Thomas Tuchel \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi: &ldquo;Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, Hasan Salihamidzic, \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 c\u00f3 Tuchel, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tuchel\" title=\"HLV Tuchel\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/2/13/arsenal-da-chot-xong-nguoi-thay-hlv-wenger.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Tuchel \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u1ee9 6 v\u1eeba qua, Salihamidzic c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Tuchel, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t CLB \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o. Bayern ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, b\u1edfi Tuchel c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng CLB ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p d\u00e0nh cho m\u00ecnh&rdquo;, Rummenigge ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Rummenigge, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng HLV Tuchel \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t CLB m\u1edbi. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-phap/psg-tinh-cuop-thomas-tuchel-truoc-mui-arsenal-197-182862.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft PSG</strong></span>, b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1t c\u1ef1u HLV Dortmund nh\u1ea5t. Ngo\u00e0i PSG th\u00ec Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Tuchel.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"690","checkdouble":"183297"},{"date":"09:21 01/04","title":"Sau Coutinho, Barca l\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u1ea3 Salah","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/31/sau-coutinho-barca-lai-muon-co-them-ca-salah.JPG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.clo