555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Barca mua Mohamed Salah, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2>Salah \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/liverpool-2.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Liverpool</strong></span> b\u1ecf ra 37 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Mohamed Salah t\u1eeb Roma v\u00e0o H\u00e8 2017, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield, l\u00fac n\u00e0y anh \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mua Mohamed Salah voi gia khung, Liverpool lo lang hinh anh\" title=\"Barca mua Mohamed Salah v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng, Liverpool lo l\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/31/sau-coutinho-barca-lai-muon-co-them-ca-salah.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Salah \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nSalah ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Crystal Palace \u1edf v\u00f2ng 32 Premier League, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a anh gi\u00fap Liverpool \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 2-1. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9 37 tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 t\u00ednh ri\u00eang \u1edf Premier League c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSalah \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp c\u0169ng \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y V\u00e0ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Messi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, c\u1ef1u sao Roma th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real v\u00e0 Barca \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec Salah</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/mohamed-salah-148052.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Salah</strong></span> gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Real \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Liverpool thay Gareth Bale. Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng Real \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tien ve Mohamed Salah\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mohamed Salah\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/18/Real-Madrid-muon-dua-Mohamed-Salah-roi-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca mua Mohamed Salah \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nBarca mua Mohamed Salah, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. T\u1edd Express kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp. Sau khi Atletico Madrid tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Antoine Griezmann cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111i t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n Salah, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/barcelona-37.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Barca </strong></span>ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 Dembele ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Sau khi c\u00f3 Coutinho, Barca mua Mohamed Salah ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn khi\u1ebfn NHM Liverpool lo l\u1eafng. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn cam k\u1ebft g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"689","checkdouble":"183294"},{"date":"11:03 01/04","title":"Barca h\u00f2a v\u1ebb vang Sevilla: Nhi\u1ec7t li\u1ec7t hoan h\u00f4 \u201cValvelona\u201d!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/1/sevilla-vs-barcelona-nhiet-liet-hoan-ho-valvelona.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor