pacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd tho\u00e1t thua trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 7 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<h2><strong>Barca tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi!</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec nh\u1ea7m l\u1eabn \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Ramon S\u00e1nchez Pizjuan. H\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p Sevilla si\u00eau sao <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-messi-giai-cuu-barca-du-chua-khoi-chan-thuong-180-183282.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Lionel Messi</strong></span> trong 57 ph\u00fat c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t gi\u00e0u \u00fd ngh\u0129a t\u1ea1i La Liga. H\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 t\u1edbi 11 \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 sao ch\u1ee9? C\u1ee9 th\u1eafng c\u00e1i \u0111\u00e3, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u00ednh sau. Champions League? M\u1eb7c k\u1ec7! Si\u00eau sao l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i duy nh\u1ea5t, ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng, ch\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 g\u00ec.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u1ee9 n\u00f3i Barca ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt m\u1edbi h\u00f2a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sevilla. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u1ecd nh\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9. N\u00e0y nh\u00e9, n\u1ebfu Messi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra? \u0110ang c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 c\u00e1i g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 to t\u00e1t, t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t hay kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng. Quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n th\u00e1i kia m\u00e0? M\u00e0 Messi c\u0169ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p th\u00eam Sevilla 40 ph\u00fat \u0111i b\u1ed9 n\u1eefa kia m\u00e0. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00f2n \u0111au \u0111\u00e2u, anh \u1ea5y c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh l\u00e0m v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sevilla vs Barca Nhiet liet hoan ho Valvelona hinh anh\" title=\"Sevilla vs Barca Nhi\u1ec7t li\u1ec7t hoan h\u00f4 Valvelona h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/Sevilla-vs-Barca-Nhiet-liet-hoan-ho-Valvelona-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Barca \u0103n m\u1eebng sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Sevilla</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau c\u00f9ng, Barca c\u0169ng c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 \u0103n m\u1eebng nh\u01b0 m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1eebng ai n\u00f3i h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. D\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u00e9p &ldquo;ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc&rdquo; nh\u01b0 n\u1eeda qu\u1ea3 cam \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o m\u00e1y xay, d\u00f9 ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n trong su\u1ed1t 87 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, d\u00f9 HLV Valverde tr\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1edbi \u0111i ch\u1eefa b\u1ec7nh v\u1ec1, ch\u1eb3ng sao c\u1ea3. H\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eeba thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n t\u1ea1i La Liga bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 &ldquo;kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3&rdquo; Leganes l\u00e0 vui l\u1eafm r\u1ed3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi xin \u0111\u1eebng nh\u1eafc nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn Johan Cruyff l\u00e0m g\u00ec. Chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 qua h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3 tr\u00f4i qua. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee9c th\u1eddi m\u1edbi l\u00e0 trang tu\u1ea5n ki\u1ec7t. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi \u00f4ng cha l\u00e0m quan l\u1edbn, l\u1edbp con ch\u00e1u sau n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tr\u1ed9m m\u1ea1t h\u1ea1ng c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i \u1ea7m \u0129. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta n\u00f3i g\u00ec th\u00ec c\u1ee9 n\u00f3i cho \u0111\u00e3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u1edbng c\u00e1i th\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sevilla vs Barca Layun\" title=\"Sevilla vs Barca Layun\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/Sevilla-vs-Barca-Layun.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, kh\u00f4ng sao</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKi\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec? Barca nh\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ebft cho Sevilla. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia m\u1eb7c cho b\u00ean kia b\u1eafn ph\u00e1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. Vi\u1ec7c Sevilla ghi c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n l\u00e0 do h\u1ecd d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi, \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i Barca c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh ch\u01a1i tr\u00f2 &ldquo;kh\u00e1ch l\u1ea5n ch\u1ee7&rdquo;. M\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Valverde ch\u1eb3ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi g\u1ea5p 3, g\u1ea5p 4 l\u1ea7n s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u1ea5y ch\u1ee9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u00f3, Barca ngay c\u1ea3 khi \u0111ang ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n, th\u1eeba \u0111\u1ee7 ni\u1ec1m tin \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n tr\u00e1i cam v\u00e0 m\u00e1y xay s\u1ebd c\u00f2n l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i n\u1eefa, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 c\u1ee9 y\u00ean t\u00e2m. Ph\u00fat 88 v\u00e0 89, Barca m\u1edbi ch\u1ecbu ghi b\u00e0n. N\u1ebfu thua 7, 8 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 80 tr\u1edf \u0111i, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec to t\u00e1t. Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Barca, \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vui, theo ki\u1ec3u b\u1ed7ng d\u01b0ng&hellip; mu\u1ed1n c\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ee9 ch\u1eb3ng sai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-messi-giai-cuu-barca-du-chua-khoi-chan-thuong-180-183282.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/1/tiet-lo-messi-giai-cuu-barca-du-chua-khoi-chan-thuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-messi-giai-cuu-barca-du-chua-khoi-chan-thuong-180-183282.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Messi gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Barca d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a kh\u1ecfi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span><br>\r\n<span>HLV Valverde x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Lionel Messi \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Sevilla v\u1eeba qua.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2><strong>Valverde qu\u00e1 gi\u1ecfi!</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\nErnesto Valverde th\u1eeba bi\u1ebft Bongda24h.vn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch m\u00ecnh su\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ta th\u00ec ta c\u1ee9 \u0111i. \u0110\u1ebfn nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i \u00f4ng ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh. Valverde, \u00f4ng gi\u1ecfi h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ngh\u0129. \u0110\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/ket-qua-sevilla-vs-barca-tran-dau-vong-30-la-liga-201718-180-183252.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Sevilla vs Barca</strong></span> n\u00e0y, \u00e1nh m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi t\u1eeb \u00f4ng m\u1edbi t\u1ecfa ra r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, Valverde ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 sai l\u1ea7m khi t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; v\u1edbi Philippe Coutinho hay Ousmane Dembele. T\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb h\u01a1n 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 r\u1ebb m\u1ea1t \u0111i. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i: Ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a n\u1ea5y m\u00e0. T\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Coutinho v\u00e0 Dembele th\u00ec ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft c\u1ea3. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1eadc trung th\u00f4i ch\u1ee9 ch\u1eb3ng h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde\" title=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/18/Goc-nhin-Tu-khi-nao,-Barca-coi-ti-hon-nhu-khong-lo-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ng\u1ea3 m\u0169 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Valverde sau tr\u1eadn Sevilla vs Barcelona</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nG\u1ea7n c\u1ea3 n\u0103m tr\u1eddi, Coutinho v\u00e0 Dembele m\u1edbi ghi c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng c\u00f3 4 b\u00e0n cho Barca th\u00f4i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, n\u00e0o li\u00ean quan g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn HLV. Nh\u00ecn Messi k\u00eca, g\u1ea7n 4 ch\u1ee5c b\u00e0n m\u00f9a n\u00e0y r\u1ed3i. \u00c0 m\u00e0 g\u1ea7n ch\u1ee5c n\u0103m r\u1ed3i, c\u00f3 khi n\u00e0o anh \u1ea5y ghi \u00edt h\u01a1n th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e2u nh\u1ec9?<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u00ean t\u1eafc l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc, nh\u1eefng si\u00eau sao nh\u01b0 v\u1eady th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu. Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ea5y c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o th\u00f4i, \u0111i b\u1ed9 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9 c\u00f3 sao \u0111\u00e2u. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta v\u1eabn n\u00f3i Barca = Thi\u00ean t\u00e0i Messi + 10 t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng. Nh\u01b0ng trong \u0111\u00f3 thi\u1ebfu m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t thi\u00ean t\u00e0i kh\u00e1c: Valverde.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-sevilla-vs-barca-01h45-ngay-14-la-liga-201718-372-183241.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/30/ket-qua-sevilla-vs-barca-tran-dau-vong-30-la-liga-201718.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-sevilla-vs-barca-01h45-ngay-14-la-liga-201718-372-183241.html\">Sevilla 2-2 Barca (KT): Tho\u00e1t thua ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c nh\u1edd song s\u00e1t Messi vs Suarez</span><br>\r\n<span>T\u1eeb ch\u1ed7 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn hai b\u00e0n, Barca gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a 2-2 nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Messi.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1i c\u00e1ch \u00f4ng \u1ea5y gi\u00fap Barca b\u1ecb Sevilla &ldquo;tra t\u1ea5n&rdquo; trong su\u1ed1t h\u01a1n 85 ph\u00fat \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt d\u1eady g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 ch\u1ec9 trong 2 ph\u00fat r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c. &ldquo;S\u01b0\u1edbng&rdquo; l\u00e2u hay kh\u00f4ng, kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng, m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 gi\u1ed1ng nhau c\u1ea3. Sau c\u00f9ng, t\u00e0i thuy\u1ebft gi\u00e1o c\u1ee7a Valverde x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1eadc th\u1ea7y. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 Messi ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0o s\u00e2n d\u00f9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u01b0a l\u00e0nh?<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo ngu\u1ed3n tin m\u1eadt m\u00e0 Bongda24h.vn thu th\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, n\u1ed9i dung l\u1eddi nh\u1eafn nh\u1ee7 Valverde g\u1eedi t\u1edbi Messi b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n nh\u01b0 sau: &ldquo;<em>Messi, v\u00e0o s\u00e2n th\u00f4i! C\u1eadu c\u1ee9 \u1edf ngo\u00e0i th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta l\u1ea1i troll cho \u0111\u1ea5y. C\u1eadu ng\u1ed3i nh\u00ecn Argentina thua 1-6 T\u00e2y Ban Nha, c\u00f2n t\u00f4i th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Barca thua \u0111\u1eadm th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e2u nh\u00e9.</em>&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi chan thuong phai vao san\" title=\"Messi chan thuong phai vao san\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/sevilla-vs-barcelona-nhiet-liet-hoan-ho-valvelona.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o s\u00e2n d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 khi c\u00f3 Messi phi th\u01b0\u1eddng, Barca c\u1ee7a Valverde m\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng. \u0110\u1eebng n\u00f3i Valverde may m\u1eafn khi c\u00f3 Messi trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hay vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 l\u1ea7n trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft l\u00e0 Valencia (b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i sau n\u1eeda n\u0103m), c\u00f9ng Olympiakos thua c\u1ea3 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Barca. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ec7nh!<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00e0o ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Messi, \u0111\u1ebfn Sergio Busquets t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1ec9 k\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n sau t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League, Valverde c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u1ed1 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kia m\u00e0. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-sevilla-vs-barca-01h45-ngay-14-la-liga-201718-372-183241.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Sevilla vs Barca</strong></span>, ai c\u0169ng th\u1ea5y Valverde c\u1ee9 ng\u1ed3i y\u00ean tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n, \u0111\u00f4i l\u00fac m\u1eb7t t\u00e1i nh\u1ee3t c\u1ea3 \u0111i. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt th\u00ec \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i h\u01a1n ch\u00fang ta t\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nValverde \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng! \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00eau cao nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m g\u01b0\u01a1ng &ldquo;t\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ebf&rdquo; t\u1ea1i Barca. Messi hay Busquets c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ed1ng n\u1ea1ng m\u1edbi ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00e2n. V\u1eady m\u00e0 h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i hay, v\u1eabn g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap Barca c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi Messi hay Busquets t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u0169ng l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh Valverde ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb cho h\u1ecd m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Tin t\u00f4i \u0111i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nHoan h\u00f4 Barca, hoan h\u00f4 Valverde! C\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng: <strong>Ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng ng\u00e0y C\u00e1 th\u00e1ng t\u01b0</strong>!<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nSevilla (4-2-3-1): </strong>Rico; Mercado (Layun 46'), Kjaer, Lenglet, Escudero; N'Zonzi, Banega; Navas (Nolito 81'), Vazquez, Correa (Pizarro); Muriel.<br>\r\n<strong>Barcelona (4-3-3): </strong>Stegen; Roberto, Pique, Umtiti, Alba; Paulinho (Denis Suarez 77'), Rakitic, Iniesta (Alcacer 81'); Dembele (Messi 58'), Luis Suarez, Coutinho.&nbsp; <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Sevilla 2-2 Barca (V\u00f2ng 30 La Liga 2017/18):</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/1/sevilla-2-2-barca.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Barcelona tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/phan-doi-loi-choi-barca-thoi-valverde-la-trach-nhiem-cua-cules-180-182988.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: Ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i &ldquo;Valvelona&rdquo; l\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c cules</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-nhin-loi-choi-real-va-barca-180-182545.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: \u0110\u00e2y Real v\u00e0 Bernabeu, kia Barca v\u00e0 Camp Nou&hellip;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/barca-vuot-qua-chelsea-ban-len-xac-chet-co-gi-dang-tung-ho-184-182176.html\">Barca v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Chelsea: B\u1eafn l\u00ean &ldquo;x\u00e1c ch\u1ebft&rdquo;, c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng tung h\u00f4?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-nhin-tu-khi-nao-loi-choi-barca-thoi-valverde-coi-ti-hon-nhu-khong-lo-180-181877