height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Las Palmas v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0, HLV Zidane mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em ni\u1ec1m tin tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu. T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a HLV Zidane c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n b\u1ecb \u0111e d\u1ecda nh\u01b0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Las Palmas, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u2013 Zidane mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cV\u00e2ng, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0o. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a CLB v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn th\u1eed th\u00e1ch.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 18 n\u0103m, t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c CLB n\u00e0y v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c. T\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i th\u00edch, v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ai \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecfi r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng, th\u00ec c\u00f3. T\u00f4i y\u00eau th\u00edch c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Zidane mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid\" title=\"Zidane mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/Zidane-muon-o-lai-Real-Madrid-o-mua-giai-sau-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Zidane mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng hi\u1ec7n nay, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng v\u1eabn b\u1ecb Barcelona b\u1ecf c\u00e1ch 15 \u0111i\u1ec3m, v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 h\u1ebft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. \u1ede Champions League, h\u1ecd \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Juventus, sau khi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc PSG \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua La Liga, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Cup Nh\u00e0 vua qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm khi\u1ebfn Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u0103ng hoa trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c \u00e9p \u0111\u00e8 n\u1eb7ng l\u00ean Zidane, trong vi\u1ec7c duy tr\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. \u0110\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf cho \u00f4ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, HLV n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 t\u1ea1i La Liga. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, Zidane \u0111\u00e3 an \u1ee7i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Isco khi cho r\u1eb1ng vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a anh r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. Tuy v\u1eady, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, v\u00e0 Isco c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, n\u1ebfu Zidane mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u1edbi th\u1eed th\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp theo mang t\u00ean Juventus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/1/las-palmas-vs-real-madrid.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/thay-gi-sau-tran-dau-las-palmas-vs-real-madrid-180-183260.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/1/thay-gi-sau-tran-dau-las-palmas-vs-real-madrid.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/thay-gi-sau-tran-dau-las-palmas-vs-real-madrid-180-183260.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau khi \u201cReal Madrid B\u201d th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm Las Palmas?</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 chi ti\u1ebft n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt khi Real Madrid \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Las Palmas v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh \u2013 B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"687","checkdouble":"183299"},{"date":"12:55 01/04","title":"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, sao Real v\u1eabn b\u1ecb Zidane ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/1/hlv-zinedine-zidane-phat-bieu-ve-gareth-bale.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color