er:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 m\u1edbi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Real Madrid v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Las Palmas, Gareth Bale v\u1eabn nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng t\u1eeb HLV Zinedine Zidane.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Las Palmas t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 30 La Liga, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. Trong \u0111\u00f3, Gareth Bale tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, HLV Zinedine Zidane v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales s\u1ebd c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ngh\u1ec9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n, Gareth Bale v\u00e0 Karim Benzema \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. H\u1ecd ghi c\u1ea3 3 b\u00e0n cho Real, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 tr\u00ean BXH La Liga v\u1edbi 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u00f3m kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Champions League. Ri\u00eang Bale c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap \u1edf c\u00e1c ph\u00fat 26 v\u00e0 51.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Zinedine Zidane phat bieu ve Gareth Bale sau tran Las Palmas hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Zinedine Zidane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale sau tr\u1eadn Las Palmas h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/hlv-zinedine-zidane-phat-bieu-ve-gareth-bale.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\">HLV Zinedine Zidane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale r\u1ea5t \u00fap m\u1edf<br>\r\n            </span></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Zinedine Zidane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale v\u1eabn kh\u00e1 d\u00e8 d\u1eb7t. \u201cT\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Bale\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cNh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd xem li\u1ec7u c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 3 t\u1edbi hay kh\u00f4ng (vs Juventus t\u1ea1i Turin)\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i La Liga v\u00e0 l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 h\u1ed3i sinh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. V\u00e0 HLV Zidane h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. \u201cKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. Nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n sau khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Ban \u0111\u1ea7u, m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 ch\u00fat ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong hi\u1ec7p 2, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng. D\u00f9 sao, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00ec sau \u0111\u1ee3t ngh\u1ec9 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Las Palmas\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Real Madrid tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/vuot-qua-nhuoc-tieu-zidane-doi-perez-dam-bao-tuong-lai-180-183299.html\">V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u, Zidane \u0111\u00f2i Perez \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/thay-gi-sau-tran-dau-las-palmas-vs-real-madrid-180-183260.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau khi \u201cReal Madrid B\u201d th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm Las Palmas?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ket-qua-las-palmas-vs-real-madrid-tran-dau-vong-30-la-liga-201718-180-183240.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Las Palmas vs Real Madrid tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 30 La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-las-palmas-vs-real-madrid-23h30-ngay-311-la-liga-201718-372-183232.html\">Las Palmas 0-3 Real Madrid (KT): V\u1eafng Ronaldo, Los Blancos v\u1eabn th\u1eafng to</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/isco-roi-real-madrid-zidane-co-phai-la-thu-pham-180-183173.html\">Isco r\u1eddi Real Madrid, Zidane c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea1m?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"686","checkdouble":"183302"},{"date":"13:28 01/04","title":"Barca nh\u1eafm \u201ch\u00e0ng hot\u201d ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba M.U cu\u1ed7m Umtiti","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/1/barca-mua-lucas-hernandez-cua-atletico-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;fon