3n tin t\u1eeb t\u1edd Don Balon, Barcelona nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/arsenal-va-real-gap-kho-vu-hau-ve-cua-atletico-180-183052.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Lucas Hernandez c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid</strong></span> nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p h\u1eefu \u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Blaugrana tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 mang anh v\u1ec1 c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Barca v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Samuel Umtiti gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 60 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh tr\u1edf n\u00ean qu\u00e1 \u00edt \u1ecfi. Barca hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang r\u1ea5t s\u1ee3 s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t Umtiti khi nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Man United d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t cho anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuyen nhuong Barca mua Lucas Hernandez cua Atletico Madrid  hinh anh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca mua Lucas Hernandez c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/14/Chuyen-nhuong-Barca-mua-Lucas-Hernandez-cua-Atletico-Madrid--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca s\u1ee3 Umtiti s\u1ebd ra \u0111i h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u0129 nhi\u00ean, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barca l\u00e0 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Umtiti \u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e2u d\u00e0i. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/xuat-hien-rao-can-cho-chuyen-nhuong-barca-mua-griezmann-180-182919.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca</strong></span> ng\u1ed3i y\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng. Theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Blaugrana \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Lucas Hernandez c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u1ea5t trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHernandez kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u. D\u00f9 m\u1edbi 22 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i 1 c\u1ee7a Atletico. Anh s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch Barca nh\u01b0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0111o\u1ea1n ng\u1eafn v\u00e0 nh\u00e3n quan kh\u00e1 s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Lucas Hernandez\" title=\"trung ve Lucas Hernandez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/barca-mua-lucas-hernandez-cua-atletico-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\">Barca mua Lucas Hernandez c\u1ee7a Atletico thay th\u1ebf<br>\r\n            </span></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 Atletico v\u00e0 Hernandez. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ea3 trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup 2018 kh\u1edfi tranh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh Barca mua Lucas Hernandez c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u1ea9n tr\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01a1n. Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Camp Nou mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng trong m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng, tr\u00e1nh \u0111i v\u00e0o v\u1ebft xe \u0111\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Neymar sang PSG. Sau khi si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil d\u1ee9t \u00e1o ra \u0111i d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, ph\u00eda Barca ph\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1ng cu\u1ed3ng t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf v\u00e0 c\u0169ng b\u1ecb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u00e9p gi\u00e1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sau-coutinho-barca-lai-muon-co-them-ca-salah-180-183294.html\">Sau Coutinho, Barca l\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u1ea3 Salah</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-chelsea-mua-toby-alderweireld-cung-mu-va-barca-172-183178.html\">V\u00ec trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng, Chelsea tuy\u00ean chi\u1ebfn M.U v\u00e0 Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-quyet-canh-tranh-voi-mu-vu-sao-chelsea-172-183113.html\">Barca quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi M.U v\u1ee5 sao Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/shaw-duoc-dem-lam-vat-te-than-de-mourinho-mua-sao-barca-172-183111.html\">Shaw \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em l\u00e0m v\u1eadt t\u1ebf th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 Mourinho mua sao Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldinho-giai-thich-nguyen-nhan-bo-mu-chon-barca-184-183012.html\">Ronaldinho gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n b\u1ecf MU, ch\u1ecdn Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"685","checkdouble":"183303"},{"date":"12:38 01/04","title":"Wenger b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec qu\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/16/wenger-bi-chi-trich-vi-qua-thanh-cong.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3