c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng th\u1eddi gian bao l\u00e2u, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t HLV \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh? T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi quan \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3. Arsene Wenger \u0111ang l\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh, gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u, \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7&rdquo; &ndash; Paul Lambert ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Arsene Wenger b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec qu\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng?\" title=\"HLV Arsene Wenger\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/26/Monaco-ngan-can-HLV-Leonardo-Jardim-toi-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Arsene Wenger b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec qu\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 Arsenal l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e0 suy tho\u00e1i. T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd l\u01a1 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng b\u1edfi h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c v\u00e0o Europa League, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 n\u1ebfu v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 Champions League. H\u1ecd t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Arsenal v\u1eabn duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, s\u1edf h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Man City, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Arsenal l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh. D\u00f9 v\u1eady tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi h\u1ecd, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Stoke l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1eed th\u00e1ch v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Stoke \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh n\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u1edf 8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Arsenal s\u1ebd l\u00e0nh \u00edt d\u1eef nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n Paul Lambert.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, HLV Arsene Wenger v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ti\u1ebfp theo, qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t cho v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Europa League v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-vs-stoke-19h30-ngay-0104-quyet-tam-rua-han-172-183281.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/30/arsenal-vs-stoke-19h30-ngay-0104-quyet-tam-rua-han.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-vs-stoke-19h30-ngay-0104-quyet-tam-rua-han-172-183281.html\">Arsenal vs Stoke (19h30 ng\u00e0y 01/04): Quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eeda h\u1eadn</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal vs Stoke t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 32 Premier League l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 tr\u1ea3 m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 thua 0-1 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"684","checkdouble":"183301"},{"date":"14:10 01/04","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! \u1ee8ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd thay th\u1ebf Conte t\u1ea1i Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/18/conte-bi-chelsea-sa-thai-va-pochettino-thay-the.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border: