ac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea xem \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Antonio Conte l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh \u00f4ng.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i nay, Chelsea s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Tottenham t\u1edbi s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 32 Premier League. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong t\u1ed1p 4 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Champions League. Theo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, n\u1ebfu Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 thua Spurs, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Antonio Conte b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. V\u00e0 \u00e9o le thay, trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Mauricio Pochettino s\u1ebd th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 \u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 sa s\u00fat \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a Chelsea. T\u1eeb nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tranh ch\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong t\u1ed1p 4 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Champions League. Nguy c\u01a1 Antonio Conte b\u1ecb Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 xa x\u00f4i. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Mauricio Pochettino c\u1ee7a Tottenham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Antonio Conte bi Chelsea sa thai va Pochettino thay the hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Antonio Conte b\u1ecb Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i v\u00e0 Pochettino thay th\u1ebf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/18/conte-bi-chelsea-sa-thai-va-pochettino-thay-the.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Conte b\u1ecb Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00d4ng ch\u1ee7 Roman Abramovich \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn ghen t\u1ecb t\u1edbi Tottenham khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Pochettino d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u song lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge l\u00fac 22h t\u1ed1i nay c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem nh\u01b0 b\u00e0i test v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u00e9o le \u1edf ch\u1ed7 n\u1ebfu Pochettino c\u00f9ng Tottenham v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Chelsea, v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u00f4ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Champions League. Tr\u00ean BXH l\u00fac n\u00e0y, The Blues \u0111ang k\u00e9m Spurs t\u1edbi 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng th\u00f4i, b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i l\u1edbn trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng danh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u s\u1ebd thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ngay c\u1ea3 khi gi\u00fap Chelsea \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Tottenham v\u00e0 xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong t\u1ed1p 4 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u, ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc Conte \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Paris Saint-Germain c\u00f9ng \u0110T Italia r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n Conte ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Chelsea tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-vs-tottenham-22h00-ngay-14-dai-chien-thoi-mat-gia-172-183291.html\">Chelsea vs Tottenham (22h00 ng\u00e0y 1/4): \u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eddi m\u1ea5t gi\u00e1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-cua-newcastle-172-183287.html\">Chelsea chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Newcastle</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-conte-noi-gi-truoc-kha-nang-bi-chelsea-sa-thai-172-183278.html\">HLV Conte n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/truoc-dai-chien-conte-thua-nhan-thua-kem-tottenham-172-183234.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn, Conte th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn thua k\u00e9m Tottenham</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-chelsea-mua-toby-alderweireld-cung-mu-va-barca-172-183178.html\">V\u00ec trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng, Chelsea tuy\u00ean chi\u1ebfn M.U v\u00e0 Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"683","checkdouble":"183306"},{"date":"14:57 01/04","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Arsenal 0-0 Stoke (H1): V\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1 v\u1eeba ngh\u0129 Europa League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://st