,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><p><strong>M\u00e0n r\u1ef1c s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Icardi v\u00e0 Immobile \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 30 khi\u1ebfn cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua top 4 \u1edf Serie A ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/3/31/ffstp.MP4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</strong></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, Serie A s\u1ebd c\u00f3 4 su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 Champions League. S\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua top 4 \u1edf x\u1ee9 s\u1edf m\u1ef3 \u1ed1ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng. Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u BXH l\u00e0 Juventus v\u00e0 Napoli, hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4 CLB kh\u00e1c s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tranh 2 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Roma, Inter Milan, Lazio v\u00e0 AC Milan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede v\u00f2ng 30 cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua top 4 \u1edf Serie A ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra ng\u00e3 r\u1ebd m\u1edbi b\u1edfi 2 trong s\u1ed1 4 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh, Inter Milan v\u00e0 Lazio \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Inter ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Hellas Verona v\u1edbi kh\u00ed th\u1ebf t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng sau m\u00e0n h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Sampdoria 5-0. Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o xanh - \u0111en ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 nh\u1edd m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/180331_224921_656.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau c\u00fa poker v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Sampdoria, Icardi l\u1ea1i m\u1edf ra chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Inter Milan v\u1edbi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. H\u01a1n 10 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, Nerazzurri nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t nh\u1edd pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Ivan Perisic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 song Inter Milan v\u1eabn t\u1ea1o ra th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Hellas Verona v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u00eam 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Mauro Icardi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng song Inter Milan ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \"c\u1eaft \u0111u\u00f4i\" Lazio b\u1edfi \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t t\u00e2n binh Benevento v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 6-2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m Mauro Icardi, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ciro Immobile c\u0169ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. V\u1edbi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 c\u00f2n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ghi th\u00eam 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Felipe Caicedo, Stefan De Vrij, Lucas Leiva v\u00e0 Luis Alberto.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng n\u00e0y, Lazio v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u00e1m s\u00e1t Inter Milan v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch ch\u1ec9 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy v\u1eady, so v\u1edbi Nerazzurri, Lazio \u0111ang \u1edf th\u1ebf b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 1 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n r\u1ef1c s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Icardi v\u00e0 Immobile c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 gay c\u1ea5n trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi. V\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, Immobile v\u1eabn \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ed9i bom v\u1edbi 26 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Tuy v\u1eady, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa anh v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 (Icardi) ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"679","checkdouble":"183255"},{"date":"06:53 01/04","title":"Juventus 3-1 AC Milan: \u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \"k\u1ebb th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/1/juventus-31-ac-milan-dang-cap-ke-thong-tri.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@