l,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n v\u1eeba quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi VCK U20 World Cup, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tony Tu\u1ea5n Anh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u Tony Tu\u1ea5n Anh, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng U20 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m U20 World Cup 2017.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Hoang Anh Tuan goi sao tung lo hen U20 World Cup vao U19 Viet hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n g\u1ecdi sao t\u1eebng l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n U20 World Cup v\u00e0o U19 Vi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/3/30/HLV-Hoang-Anh-Tuan-goi-sao-tung-lo-hen-U20-World-Cup-vao-U19-Viet-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n g\u1ecdi Tony Tu\u1ea5n Anh\u00a0v\u00e0o \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tony Tu\u1ea5n Anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n xa l\u1ea1 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. C\u00f2n nh\u1edb t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ee3t\u00a0t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n \u1edf Nha Trang v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 3/2017, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 xin t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng U20 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 World Cup U20 t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. \u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3, Tu\u1ea5n Anh l\u1ea1i g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n U20 VN.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trao th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho ch\u00e0ng trai sinh n\u0103m 1999. V\u1edbi th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng (cao 1m80, n\u1eb7ng 70 kg), Tu\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Tu\u1ea5n Anh \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB U19 Bojemians Praha \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m. Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t trong vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng g\u1ecdn gh\u1ebd, nh\u00e3n quan chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh ra v\u00e0 l\u1edbn l\u00ean t\u1ea1i CH S\u00e9c h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u1edbi cho c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ngay sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi bay sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 4/4 t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ed5 \u00edch gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp c\u1ecd x\u00e1t, n\u00e2ng cao n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u00e0 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup 2019.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"677","checkdouble":"183269"},{"date":"05:57 01/04","title":"HLV FC Seoul ng\u1ee3i khen tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 G\u0110KT HAGL","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/1/hlv-fc-seoul-ngoi-khen-trinh-do-gdkt-hagl.jpg","new_de