ckground-position:-48px -224px}.ui-icon-gripsmall-diagonal-se{background-position:-64px -224px}.ui-icon-grip-diagonal-se{background-position:-80px -224px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-tl{border-top-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc, HLV \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb FC Seoul \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ng\u1ee3i khen cho b\u1eadc ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i \u0111ang gi\u1eef ch\u1ee9c G\u0110KT HAGL, \u00f4ng Chung Hae Soung.<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i U19 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i U19 FC Seoul \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Gia Lai trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U19 HAGL c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Chonburi, Mito Hollyhock v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecbu v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec chung cu\u1ed9c sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, G\u0110KT HAGL, \u00f4ng Chung Hae Soung \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho BHL U19 FC Seoul. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Myung Jinyoung \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV FC Seoul ngoi khen trinh do GDKT HAGL hinh anh\" title=\"HLV FC Seoul ng\u1ee3i khen tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 G\u0110KT HAGL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/dlap0817_pchh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV U19 FC Seoul \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c\u00a0G\u0110KT HAGL Chung Hae Soung</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng U19 FC Seoul t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: \u201cNh\u1eefng t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a \u201cth\u1ea7y\u201d Chung r\u1ea5t b\u1ed5 \u00edch, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 cho b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i m\u00e0 cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng t\u1eebng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat khi g\u1eb7p th\u1ea7y Chung, v\u00ec t\u1eeb khi \u00f4ng sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u00edt c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u00e1p chuy\u1ebfn bay v\u1ec1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ed1i 31/3, v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng c\u00f9ng ng\u00e0y to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i U19 FC Seoul \u0111\u00e3 tranh th\u1ee7 l\u00ean Trung t\u00e2m hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n H\u00e0m R\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i K-League tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 4/4.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, G\u0110KT Chung Hae Soung \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb U19 FC Seoul t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ecd x\u00e1t \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m h\u00e0nh trang ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Myung Jinyoung \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 gi\u1ea3i U21. V\u1ecb n\u00e0y cho hay: \u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f2n t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c 1 gi\u1ea3i tr\u1ebb qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf r\u1ea5t hay n\u1eefa l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i U21 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf B\u00e1o Thanh Ni\u00ean cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay. T\u00f4i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i U19 FC Seoul r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay. U19 FC Seoul s\u1ebd t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00eam v\u00e0i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed U21 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a CLB FC Seoul \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p K-League \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i\u201d .<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em><strong>Highlight U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 U19 Seoul</strong></em></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/3/24/Highlight-U19-Viet-Nam-vs-U19-U19-Seoul-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ea1nh C\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"676","checkdouble":"183270"}]}